quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  92,15,"Yanngataaka e nguli ngee yiite si wonah ɓurɗo hiiteede oon woni keefeero."
  92,16,"Oon pennuɗo ko nelaaɗo-yo o his- addi ko, o ɗuurnii gollirde yamiroore Alla."
  92,17,"Ma woɗɗitonge ɓurdo hulde Alla oon woni Abuu bakri yo welu Alla won e makko."
  92,18,"Oon nafqoowo jawdi mum e geece moƴƴere ngam o laaɓa e bakkatiiji."
  92,19,"Tottirtah tottiroowo e jawdi mum ngam o yoɓa neema mbo goɗɗo neemini e dow makko."
  92,20,"Alah ko o faala ko o tottirta ko e jawdi makko si wonah Yeeso Toowɗo e dow tagu Makko."
  92,21,"Yaama o wele ko Alla tottata mbo e njobdi teddundi."
  93,1,"Alla woondirii arwannde ñalawma."
  93,2,"Alla woondirii jemma si mbo niɓɓiɗi dille aade en deeƴi."
  93,3,"joom Ma -aan nelaaɗo- accaani Ma, O tikkanaani ma, hono no sirkuɓe mbi*irata nde wahyu darii setta."
  93,4,"Ko gelle laakar ɓuri galle aduna, sabu ko mbo soomi ko e neemaaji duumiiɗi ɗi taƴandirtah."
  93,5,"Yaama joom ma okku ma baraaje aan e leñol ma haa mbeleɗa ko O okku ma ko."
  93,6,"O tawii ma ko a yatiime mbo baaba mum sankii, O tottuma moolorde, Taane Abdul Muttalibi neh ma ko noon kadi Bappa ma Abuu Taalib."
  93,7,"O tawma a anndah binndol e iimaan, O anndin ma heen ko a anndaana."
  93,8,"O taw ma ko a baasɗo O alɗin ma."
  93,9,"Woto bonnu gollodde e alyatiima baasɗo baaba makko saanga cukaagu, woto hoynu mbo."
  93,10,"Woto furo ñaagatooɗo katajinɗo."
  93,11,"Yettu neema mbo joom ma neemin ma kaala mbo."
  94,1,"Alla yaacnii ɓernde ma O yiɗnu ma jaɓɓaade wahyu."
  94,2,"Min njaafi ma ko yawti ko e bakkatuuji ma Min tellinan ma teddeendi balɗe jaahiliyya ɗe ngonnaɗa ɗe."
  94,3,"Oon tampinɗo ma haa keeci ɗesi helde."
  94,4,"Mi toownan ma jantawol ma, haa mbattuɗa inneede e noddinaandu e wuurnaandu e ka nanndi heen."
  94,5,"Sattaande ɓittere fof woni battane mum ko newuya e yaajeende e ittude nde."
  94,6,"Kala satteende e ɓittere na wondi e newaare e yaajeende, si a anndii ɗuum hulnataa ma wollo faloo noddaandu ma lorde yimɓe ma wollo falaade noddaandu Ma."
  94,7,"Si gaynii golle ma, kantinɗaa ɗe tiiɗna e dewal Alla."
  94,8,"Waɗ ndeereeru Ma e faandaare Ma faade e Alla gooto O."